kaleidoscope

Class Shape

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • kaleidoscope.Shape

  • public class Shape
extends java.util.Observable
    This is the Model class for a kaleidoscope program. It is an Observable, which means that it can notifyObservers that something in the model has changed, and they should take appropriate actions.
    Author:
    Josh Kessler, Kelley Loder, David Matuszek
